    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/4a57013c2f37611d9f4c3154d77e255c.poster.avif?t=1674032093\" width=500 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/4a57013c2f37611d9f4c3154d77e255c.webm?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/4a57013c2f37611d9f4c3154d77e255c.mp4?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>在漂亮的场景中 使用不同的战斗技巧 应对不同类型的敌人组合。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/292eaf90049a8daf4f7657a59dbbce1a.poster.avif?t=1674032093\" width=500 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/292eaf90049a8daf4f7657a59dbbce1a.webm?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/292eaf90049a8daf4f7657a59dbbce1a.mp4?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>多种神秘丰富的自然地貌与机关</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/c01f8aaf9da85261ce3e420f1a4fe79a.poster.avif?t=1674032093\" width=500 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/c01f8aaf9da85261ce3e420f1a4fe79a.webm?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/c01f8aaf9da85261ce3e420f1a4fe79a.mp4?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>拥有近战和远处两种攻击方式，使用远程武器攻击敌人弱点 或 拆除陷阱机关。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/e8a31e60eab4139e24671d4759aeb537.poster.avif?t=1674032093\" width=500 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/e8a31e60eab4139e24671d4759aeb537.webm?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837130/extras/e8a31e60eab4139e24671d4759aeb537.mp4?t=1674032093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>激发人肾上腺素的激烈BOSS战</strong><br><br>▲bilibili：@星塔星夜<br>▲交流群：839191387<br><br><strong>创作初衷：</strong><br>“我很忙，我时间不多，我想在今晚下班后体验一个<br>   完整的，漂亮的，痛快的，不强迫我看剧情的二次元动作游戏”<br><br><strong>游戏特点：</strong><br>《星塔星夜》全名&quot;星塔星夜星影院&quot;一款动作闯关游戏，按键少。<br>游戏中你将在广阔大自然中陪伴 流亡战士(茉诺)渡过关键的数小时。<br>包含即时战斗，流畅的动作，漂亮的身姿，无需旋转视角，只应对一个方向。<br><br><strong>名字的由来：</strong><br>&quot;星塔星夜星影院&quot;<br> 一个被上千座星塔围绕在中心的巨大屏幕，是给位于高空环球旅馆准备的绝佳荧屏。",
